 src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  痛攰死你都唔驚 咁仲驚咩？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nFrom過來人"},{"pid":"86c1bd826f37a8e172ed24d6a852525ff93c4af4","tid":1812681,"uid":51625,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T18:35:10.000Z","msg":"樓主，你係有咩心事？<br />\n<br />\n如果有嘅話請講出嚟，大家一齊拆掂佢啊！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d506bad2c15dd9a0b5fa36bf01ec5df85eec9712","tid":1812681,"uid":75050,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T19:04:03.000Z","msg":"一定係吸毒OD死，俗稱「爽死」，前提係你有門路同要有錢買到足夠嘅貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9beba3bf5c5ce249eb0a8b9086405fc9683888f","tid":1812681,"uid":283071,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T20:00:35.000Z","msg":"話明死 從來只有安樂死又點會有舒服死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3eb6403a87cebc67769df3621aa0e172d6b7af55","tid":1812681,"uid":154106,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T20:29:47.000Z","msg":"真主萬歲 人肉炸彈"},{"pid":"a10f2daed55653603d581bba46ad465fff2894fb","tid":1812681,"uid":159916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f1435b47f43d4066b159cc270195c233c2fd82ca","tid":1812681,"uid":36673,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"fd4d4fdefac2d28141fbd402bef6aa2e2f6c22b0","tid":1812681,"uid":314767,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:36:33.000Z","msg":"燒炭再食安眠藥？<br />\n(生命可貴 真係學術研究好 咪去試！！！)"},"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T17:39:43.000Z","msg":"燒炭缺氧係好辛苦，慘過死<br />\n一般安眠藥唔夠勁，中途會醒<br />\n仲要諗唔可以比人救返，個腦缺過氧救返=？<br />\n<br />\n真係唔好試<br />\n所以自殺方法都必然痛苦（除左安樂死）"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-05T21:38:02.000Z","msg":"吸氧氣筒？"}]}